title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 4/27 - Wolves L/Florio
description: Montage and malaise to start the show after the Wolves gave up another 4th quarter double-digit lead to lose game 5, then Mike Florio checks in pre-NFL Draft to tell us how much he hates mock drafts.
